_:N49c3c6c643c94f3db5dbf905a90e6d08 <http://schema.org/description> "The QEII Conference Centre (QEIICC) is an international events venue that hosts conferences and receptions for up to 2,500 delegates in Westminster, London. QEIICC is an executive agency, sponsored by the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government ." .
